MOST IMMEDIATE
No. 1/34/1/2004-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 23rd May, 2004
2 Jyaistha, 1926(S).
The undersigned is directed to say that Dr. Manmohan Singh has been sworn
in as the Prime Minister by the President at 1730 hours on Saturday, the 22nd May,
2004, in the Rashtrapati Bhavan, New Delhi.
2.
The Ministers as shown in the list attached were also sworn in by the
President at 1730 hours on Saturday, the 22nd May, 2004, in the Rashtrapati
Bhavan, New Delhi.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 2301 5802
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to Deputy Chairman and Members of the
Planning Commission.
